data.description: Beautiful 2-story home in the Medway Landing community of Montague Plantation!  Great open floor plan with spacious Living, Dining, & Kitchen areas, plus a versatile sitting room on the main floor.  The bright Kitchen with HUGE walk-in pantry offers granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and appealing white cabinets.  Up the staircase, you will discover a great loft - second living room.  The Master suite is sure to please with generous accommodations including a vast closet and serene bathroom with an over-sized shower.  Also upstairs are three additional bedrooms, full hall bathroom, and a large laundry room.  Invite your friends & family out back to relax on the patio, toss a football in the yard, or sit around the fire pit!   $1,700 credit available toward buyer'sclosing costs and pre-paids with acceptable offer and use of preferred lender.
